  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the safety and efficacy of gonadotropin-releasing
      hormone (GnRH) antagonist therapy versus placebo in patients with moderate to severe
      rheumatoid arthritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
