    <time_frame>By day 2, 5, 10 and 15</time_frame>
    <description>This endpoint is not directly related to clinical efficacy. Hormones include LH, FSH, oestradiol, testosterone,and cortisol. Biomarkers include immunologic markers, bone markers and cardiovascular markers. This secondary endpoint was sent to authorities during the study before unblinding.</description>
